title: The Breakfast Club Talks Brittney Griner, Bow Wow and Ask Yee
itunes:title: The Breakfast Club Talks Brittney Griner, Bow Wow and Ask Yee
description:
Today on The Breakfast Club, Yee gives us the latest on the Brittney Griner case during Front Page News. We also ask our listeners if you would tell your best friend they are getting cheated on. During The Rumor Report The Breakfast Club reacts to Angie Martinez' sit down interview with Lauren London. Charlamagne gives his Donkey of The Day and Positive Note. 

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
